WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:07.220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:07.220 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 14]

01:23.230 --> 01:24.050
Take it back.

01:24.510 --> 01:25.740
Never show your face before me again.

01:48.280 --> 01:49.290
Since you're resentful

01:50.350 --> 01:51.210
and hate seeing me,

01:52.280 --> 01:53.660
cultivate harder and surpass me.

01:55.150 --> 01:56.900
Once you're strong enough to kill me,

01:58.200 --> 01:59.660
I'll stay away from you.

02:01.790 --> 02:04.930
Otherwise, as long as I live,

02:06.400 --> 02:07.660
I won't let go.

02:08.870 --> 02:09.540
You're crazy.

02:12.710 --> 02:13.500
Trust me.

02:20.590 --> 02:21.170
Lifei,

02:23.190 --> 02:23.890
do you trust me?

02:24.360 --> 02:24.940
I do.

02:40.310 --> 02:40.980
What are you doing?

02:50.680 --> 02:51.340
I get it now.

02:52.190 --> 02:53.940
You fear my weak spirit energy will hold you back,

02:54.400 --> 02:55.890
so you're transferring your power to me in advance.

02:56.960 --> 02:58.290
I want to confirm that our Fragrance Bond

02:59.710 --> 03:00.690
can shield us.

03:09.120 --> 03:11.570
Linked by the Fragrance Bond, we live and die as one.

03:11.800 --> 03:13.260
We'll find Lu for sure.

03:52.280 --> 03:53.220
You used the forbidden art.

03:55.710 --> 03:56.940
At Xingzheng Hall,

03:58.710 --> 04:01.500
you used the Puppet Body Art on me, right?

04:13.280 --> 04:13.940
Lei Xiuyuan,

04:18.030 --> 04:19.010
do you think transferring every injury

04:19.030 --> 04:20.170
onto yourself

04:21.430 --> 04:22.540
makes up for everything?

04:25.270 --> 04:26.610
So loyal and loving of you.

04:27.680 --> 04:29.540
I never think that. I just...

04:29.560 --> 04:31.410
You just always assume you know best.

04:32.870 --> 04:35.850
You went after Riyan, joined Wuyue Court,

04:37.480 --> 04:38.850
and showed up wherever I went.

04:42.600 --> 04:45.140
You slipped the art on me secretly

04:45.680 --> 04:47.020
in the name of protecting me.

04:47.560 --> 04:48.930
You're the same as always.

04:49.800 --> 04:51.100
Why make choices for me?

04:51.680 --> 04:53.340
Why never ask if I accept this?

04:53.920 --> 04:55.140
What are you even to me?

04:55.480 --> 04:56.580
Wait, Lifei.

04:56.580 --> 04:58.490
♪The warmth within my arms♪

04:58.870 --> 05:01.910
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

05:02.750 --> 05:03.980
I can't break the Fragrance Bond.

05:03.980 --> 05:05.510
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

05:05.510 --> 05:07.290
Because I don't want to harm Tongzhou.

05:07.290 --> 05:09.240
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

05:09.680 --> 05:10.290
As for you...

05:10.290 --> 05:12.810
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

05:13.240 --> 05:15.170
I want no ties with you, not even a trace.

05:15.170 --> 05:16.330
♪I can no longer tell you♪

05:16.730 --> 05:19.480
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

05:19.480 --> 05:23.170
Take back the Puppet Body Art.

05:23.610 --> 05:25.330
♪Knowing love and hate♪

05:25.650 --> 05:29.570
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

05:31.360 --> 05:32.610
Use the heart's blood as the bond, huh?

05:32.930 --> 05:37.130
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

05:39.040 --> 05:40.930
Lifei. Lifei.

05:42.170 --> 05:45.130
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

05:46.750 --> 05:47.540
Now...

05:47.540 --> 05:48.890
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

05:49.560 --> 05:50.370
I'm returning it to you.

05:50.370 --> 05:52.370
♪I wish you well♪

05:52.690 --> 05:54.370
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

05:54.730 --> 05:58.510
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

05:58.510 --> 05:59.100
Leave.

06:00.010 --> 06:01.650
♪You're still screaming♪

06:01.930 --> 06:04.000
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

06:04.000 --> 06:05.020
Leave now!

06:06.690 --> 06:10.930
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

06:11.290 --> 06:14.130
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

06:14.450 --> 06:16.610
♪I'd shatter my soul♪

06:17.010 --> 06:21.530
♪To lay all your days in peace♪

06:21.530 --> 06:23.570
♪Who says that love and hate♪

06:23.890 --> 06:28.400
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped?♪

06:28.400 --> 06:32.760
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

06:33.120 --> 06:36.000
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

06:36.320 --> 06:42.400
♪With the light from my fingertips, I build a paradise♪

06:43.120 --> 06:46.680
♪To wander with you♪

06:49.390 --> 06:52.250
So he is Elder Guangwei's new disciple.

06:53.830 --> 06:56.460
Is he the one who broke the restriction spells before?

06:59.630 --> 07:00.220
Yes.

07:03.040 --> 07:04.780
If you never want to see him,

07:05.360 --> 07:06.850
I can report this to Master

07:06.950 --> 07:08.250
or Elder Guangwei.

07:10.240 --> 07:11.370
No need to trouble them.

07:12.190 --> 07:13.340
We're nothing to each other now.

07:14.190 --> 07:16.780
He braved all restrictions just to see you.

07:17.040 --> 07:18.140
That's not how strangers act.

07:20.480 --> 07:21.220
He won't come again.

07:31.600 --> 07:32.850
Why make choices for me?

07:33.480 --> 07:35.140
Why never ask if I accept this?

07:35.630 --> 07:36.900
What are you even to me?

07:39.750 --> 07:40.660
Leave now!

07:44.270 --> 07:44.900
Xiuyuan.

07:50.430 --> 07:51.050
Lei?

07:55.950 --> 07:56.540
Cailing.

07:58.040 --> 07:58.810
Do you realize

07:59.190 --> 08:00.660
if danger had struck just now,

08:00.950 --> 08:02.220
you couldn't have defended yourself?

08:02.560 --> 08:04.660
What troubles you? This is nothing like you.

08:15.240 --> 08:16.850
Your mind is wandering far away.

08:17.920 --> 08:18.490
Wait...

08:20.750 --> 08:22.730
Do you have feelings for Jiang Lifei?

08:39.240 --> 08:40.850
Master, Lifei is here.

08:41.510 --> 08:44.180
Hey, you've got some nerve

08:44.790 --> 08:46.890
slacking off in the daytime!

08:47.840 --> 08:49.820
Lifei, why aren't you practicing?

08:53.960 --> 08:56.100
What's wrong? Let me check.

09:02.750 --> 09:03.980
Your heart meridians are hurt.

09:06.840 --> 09:07.700
What happened?

09:09.440 --> 09:12.420
I'm fine. Just practiced too hard.

09:15.270 --> 09:16.370
See? I told you

09:17.480 --> 09:19.730
not to chase quick results.

09:20.270 --> 09:22.460
Too stubborn to listen.

09:22.790 --> 09:24.770
Starting today, at every Xu hour,

09:25.270 --> 09:26.580
meditate for four hours at Yuelian Pond

09:26.840 --> 09:28.180
behind Baicao Peak.

09:29.910 --> 09:30.820
Yuelian Pond?

09:31.790 --> 09:33.730
It's the top secret realm in Wuyue Court.

09:34.200 --> 09:36.700
Rumor says a spirit cave under the pond connects heaven and earth.

09:37.030 --> 09:38.220
By meditating on Yuelian Stone,

09:38.550 --> 09:40.580
you absorb spirit power, strengthen your body, and purify your marrow.

09:42.360 --> 09:45.580
That's incredible. Let's go together.

09:46.200 --> 09:47.250
It's a secret realm.

09:47.790 --> 09:49.580
Ordinary disciples aren't allowed there.

09:49.910 --> 09:51.940
Elder Cuixuan laid out a formation there.

09:52.270 --> 09:53.220
Without his approval,

09:53.390 --> 09:55.340
only elders may enter

09:55.360 --> 09:56.100
to heal normally.

09:56.360 --> 09:57.890
Our master is pulling strings for you.

09:58.440 --> 09:59.250
Don't say that!

09:59.440 --> 10:00.850
I never do that.

10:02.440 --> 10:04.220
Show me your jade pendant.

10:11.480 --> 10:14.770
This seal lifts the restriction. Go early and return soon.

10:15.150 --> 10:15.980
Don't delay our meals.

10:18.200 --> 10:18.700
Let's go.

10:54.200 --> 10:55.300
All spirit energy

10:55.510 --> 10:57.530
is within your every breath.

11:07.720 --> 11:10.250
Nothing is everything. Emptiness is fullness.

11:27.030 --> 11:28.010
Qin.

11:28.720 --> 11:30.010
I've come to cultivate here, too.

11:30.510 --> 11:31.700
Didn't expect to see you.

11:32.360 --> 11:34.420
If I'm intruding, I'll come another day.

11:38.480 --> 11:38.980
Yangling.

11:43.440 --> 11:45.370
Yangling, you're hurt.

11:48.670 --> 11:51.340
While I hunted the traitor down the mountain,

11:51.960 --> 11:54.490
I let my guard slip, and the traitor hurt my spirit meridians.

11:55.910 --> 11:56.730
I'll fetch my master.

11:56.910 --> 11:57.340
No.

11:58.960 --> 12:00.060
No one can learn

12:00.670 --> 12:01.890
that I'm injured.

12:02.080 --> 12:02.580
Why?

12:05.960 --> 12:08.820
I went down to investigate the disciples

12:09.910 --> 12:12.060
turning to the demonic path.

12:13.000 --> 12:15.300
The traitor is dead,

12:16.510 --> 12:18.530
yet the hidden demonic spies remain undiscovered.

12:19.240 --> 12:21.130
If they find out I'm injured,

12:21.510 --> 12:22.770
the demon clan will strike,

12:23.120 --> 12:24.250
endangering Wuyue Court.

12:25.440 --> 12:27.180
Are there demonic spies in Wuyue Court?

12:29.550 --> 12:30.490
The demon clan plans

12:30.720 --> 12:32.220
to overthrow the immortal sects

12:32.510 --> 12:34.250
and slaughter the Central Plains when the Sea Calamity arrives.

12:34.840 --> 12:35.420
Many cultivators

12:35.790 --> 12:37.700
have fallen to darkness in recent years.

12:37.870 --> 12:38.610
We must stay vigilant.

12:45.670 --> 12:48.100
Her spirit energy is so clean.

12:50.750 --> 12:51.340
Lifei.

12:53.480 --> 12:56.340
I feel bad about making you pass your spirit power to me.

12:57.790 --> 12:58.340
Are you okay?

12:58.670 --> 12:59.340
I'm fine.

13:01.910 --> 13:02.580
This thing has

13:03.360 --> 13:06.530
a mind of its own and fits you perfectly.

13:07.240 --> 13:09.060
I hope you accept it.

13:18.510 --> 13:19.340
How did you get inside?

13:20.840 --> 13:21.490
Lei.

13:23.390 --> 13:25.530
Master sent me here to practice and fix my injured meridians.

13:30.600 --> 13:32.850
Elder Guangwei really looks out for you.

13:33.270 --> 13:34.370
He's never

13:34.550 --> 13:36.370
done this for any other disciple before.

13:38.870 --> 13:40.490
Yangling, your flying ribbon.

13:42.670 --> 13:43.890
How to control it?

13:44.550 --> 13:45.340
Please show me.

13:49.870 --> 13:51.300
Sure, I'll show you.

13:52.910 --> 13:55.250
Lei, we're heading off now.

14:06.270 --> 14:07.060
Your pulse is unstable.

14:07.870 --> 14:09.940
In the strong wind in the mountains, don't use your spirit power.

14:17.080 --> 14:17.820
Stay out of this.

14:29.200 --> 14:30.340
Mr. Zuo Qiu told me

14:30.720 --> 14:32.850
to watch over Lifei when we left the academy.

14:33.750 --> 14:34.820
Do not trouble yourself, Qin.

14:35.150 --> 14:36.100
I'm taking her away right now.

14:53.440 --> 14:54.130
Lei Xiuyuan,

14:54.960 --> 14:55.580
must you ruin

14:55.600 --> 14:56.730
my belongings to feel satisfied?

15:00.750 --> 15:01.700
Calm yourself.

15:02.510 --> 15:03.980
I shall gift you another one later.

15:10.600 --> 15:11.420
My apologies.

15:11.910 --> 15:13.130
My master told me to return early.

15:13.440 --> 15:14.370
I'll seek your guidance later.

15:44.510 --> 15:46.100
Sorry, I overslept.

15:46.840 --> 15:48.180
Wait. I'll start cooking right away.

15:49.750 --> 15:50.460
Lifei,

15:51.320 --> 15:52.610
where did you get the flying ribbon?

15:53.750 --> 15:54.730
Qin gave it to me

15:54.750 --> 15:56.010
at Yuelian Pond

15:56.030 --> 15:56.730
last night.

16:00.150 --> 16:02.890
Every female disciple across Wuyue Court's

16:02.910 --> 16:04.940
sixteen peaks admires him.

16:05.270 --> 16:06.940
Yet he devotes himself to cultivation,

16:07.120 --> 16:09.580
never growing close to any female disciple.

16:09.790 --> 16:11.820
He once gave you a jade cicada,

16:11.960 --> 16:14.490
and now such a precious flying ribbon.

16:14.600 --> 16:16.820
You share quite a deep bond.

16:17.510 --> 16:18.650
Is this ribbon precious?

16:18.960 --> 16:19.610
Yes.

16:20.360 --> 16:22.980
It's Xuanyin Spirit Silk Elder Cuixuan took

16:23.150 --> 16:24.460
when they wiped out the Tiancan Sect.

16:25.080 --> 16:27.010
Zhaomin, I'm not wrong, right?

16:27.270 --> 16:28.850
Elder Cuixuan handed it

16:29.200 --> 16:30.340
down to Qin, I think.

16:31.600 --> 16:34.250
Lifei, Xuanyin Spirit Silk

16:34.390 --> 16:36.850
allows you to zip between all peaks

16:37.120 --> 16:39.100
and protect yourself when trouble comes.

16:39.960 --> 16:41.610
He is really generous to you.

16:42.390 --> 16:43.770
It's way too valuable.

16:44.120 --> 16:45.730
Go thank him now.

16:50.150 --> 16:52.730
He is probably in Wengu Hall right now.

17:28.830 --> 17:30.860
This formation can detect the location of the demonic energy.

17:31.110 --> 17:32.380
It'll respond if someone is

17:32.720 --> 17:33.900
practicing demonic arts.

17:40.350 --> 17:42.620
Qin, wait up!

17:45.480 --> 17:45.860
Qin!

17:47.400 --> 17:48.090
Qin.

17:56.750 --> 17:57.290
Qin...

18:10.830 --> 18:11.570
Qin,

18:19.400 --> 18:21.140
this Xuanyin Spirit Silk is amazing.

18:21.510 --> 18:23.570
With a little spirit energy, it flies through the wind.

18:24.550 --> 18:27.860
It's too precious for me to take it.

18:29.400 --> 18:31.620
Treasures rarely find

18:31.750 --> 18:32.730
people who fit.

18:33.400 --> 18:34.380
You got lost before,

18:34.400 --> 18:36.290
so I knew you needed this.

18:37.200 --> 18:38.090
It looks perfect on you.

18:39.790 --> 18:41.050
Thanks a lot.

18:41.640 --> 18:43.380
If you need me to run any errands later,

18:43.440 --> 18:44.250
just say the word.

18:57.680 --> 18:59.050
Ignore people who don't matter.

19:00.880 --> 19:02.010
You don't want to see him, right?

19:11.160 --> 19:12.220
Should I help you avoid him?

19:13.200 --> 19:13.730
How?

19:25.550 --> 19:27.220
Tie this spirit silk over your shoulders,

19:30.110 --> 19:31.250
and it'll make flying smoother.

19:32.790 --> 19:33.660
I can tie it myself.

19:35.640 --> 19:36.700
What are they doing?

19:36.960 --> 19:37.770
It's fine.

19:39.240 --> 19:40.050
I can handle it myself.

19:42.030 --> 19:42.940
Let me.

19:42.960 --> 19:43.810
I just...

20:00.200 --> 20:02.330
I heard that as the top disciple,

20:03.030 --> 20:04.330
you take extra good care

20:04.550 --> 20:05.420
of all new disciples

20:05.720 --> 20:06.860
and give them protective treasures.

20:08.880 --> 20:11.420
I wonder what you'll give me.

20:12.240 --> 20:13.980
Did you get any treasure when you first came?

20:14.240 --> 20:14.860
No.

20:15.510 --> 20:16.490
There are sixteen peaks.

20:16.590 --> 20:18.330
He can't have endless treasures to hand out.

20:19.240 --> 20:21.050
He probably only gives gifts to those he's close to.

20:22.240 --> 20:22.940
Could be.

20:25.240 --> 20:26.220
Yaoguang Peak has

20:26.640 --> 20:28.530
the best swords and treasures in Wuyue Court.

20:28.680 --> 20:30.810
You've won the great favor of Elder Guangwei,

20:31.070 --> 20:32.530
so I won't bother myself.

20:38.480 --> 20:40.770
Let go, hurry up!

20:45.590 --> 20:47.250
I'm from Yaoguang Peak too.

20:48.240 --> 20:51.730
Please treat me fairly and give me something.

21:03.920 --> 21:04.700
What's that?

21:09.550 --> 21:10.700
Demonic energy on Yaoguang Peak!

21:25.920 --> 21:26.900
Songfeng?

21:54.510 --> 21:55.140
Yangling!

21:57.510 --> 21:58.530
It's Songfeng.

21:58.880 --> 22:00.180
He's practicing demonic arts.

22:37.240 --> 22:37.660
Lifei.

22:37.680 --> 22:38.140
Xiuyuan.

22:38.750 --> 22:39.220
Don't come closer!

23:06.200 --> 23:06.620
Slay!

23:25.750 --> 23:27.730
- Master! - Master!

23:49.200 --> 23:50.980
As expected, it's the demon clan's evil arts.

23:53.790 --> 23:54.810
Keep searching every corner.

23:55.440 --> 23:57.460
Don't miss any hint of demonic energy.

23:58.350 --> 23:59.090
Understood.

24:03.590 --> 24:06.900
Xiuyuan, Yangling, come with me.

24:21.030 --> 24:25.460
I can't believe demon spies have snuck into our sect.

24:26.440 --> 24:29.860
Who knows how many disciples got corrupted?

24:30.750 --> 24:33.050
Every peak needs a full sweep.

24:36.720 --> 24:39.050
Guangwei, I just returned to Wuyue Court.

24:40.200 --> 24:43.810
Is he your disciple, Lei Xiuyuan?

24:46.310 --> 24:46.980
Yes.

24:48.070 --> 24:51.250
He didn't flinch or get corrupted by the demonic energy.

24:51.830 --> 24:53.180
Not only brave,

24:53.590 --> 24:56.660
but he's probably broken through the fourth level.

24:57.440 --> 25:01.770
Xiuyuan's strength is actually at the fifth level.

25:01.770 --> 25:02.610
[Baifu, Wuyue Court]

25:05.640 --> 25:06.490
Baifu,

25:07.070 --> 25:09.050
I asked you to pick new talents at Fengchu Academy,

25:09.160 --> 25:09.860
but you wouldn't go.

25:10.310 --> 25:11.220
Now look what's happened.

25:11.790 --> 25:13.220
This once-in-a-generation genius

25:13.310 --> 25:14.620
[Qingle, Wuyue Court]
got taken by Elder Guangwei.

25:15.440 --> 25:16.420
Regretting now?

25:17.720 --> 25:19.460
No, no hard feelings.

25:20.510 --> 25:23.090
He's part of Wuyue Court, anyway.

25:23.640 --> 25:25.420
Baifu's right.

25:26.200 --> 25:30.140
Facing the demons, disciples from every peak need

25:30.510 --> 25:31.570
to work together.

25:32.480 --> 25:34.250
Xiuyuan, come up here.

25:53.030 --> 25:54.290
You've mastered the basics of swordsmanship.

25:55.000 --> 25:58.620
This Longyuan Sword is our court's greatest treasure.

25:59.680 --> 26:02.530
I'm giving it to you today.

26:14.680 --> 26:15.460
Lei Xiuyuan,

26:16.030 --> 26:18.530
this sword means the world to your master.

26:19.400 --> 26:21.090
It can cut down any evil spirit or demon.

26:21.920 --> 26:23.250
Say thanks to your master.

26:37.510 --> 26:38.250
Thank you, Master.

26:41.240 --> 26:43.770
Qin got hurt fighting demons.

26:44.720 --> 26:49.250
Xiuyuan, starting today, help him lead other disciples

26:49.680 --> 26:53.490
to reinforce the formation, and stand guard against the demon clan.

26:59.750 --> 27:00.810
Understood, Master.

27:03.750 --> 27:06.980
Elder Guangwei, Lei's only been here a few months.

27:07.110 --> 27:09.980
Isn't it too much to put such an important duty on him?

27:10.400 --> 27:11.860
The Sea Calamity is almost here.

27:12.960 --> 27:15.860
We can't stick to old rules when picking capable people.

27:16.310 --> 27:19.050
Yangling, I know you're reliable and calm,

27:19.480 --> 27:20.940
but you've got to be flexible.

27:21.350 --> 27:23.770
We can bend the rules during crises.

27:24.510 --> 27:25.090
Understood.

27:41.070 --> 27:42.330
After all this time,

27:42.920 --> 27:45.860
you still haven't broken through the fifth level.

27:46.110 --> 27:47.490
Useless.

27:47.960 --> 27:50.420
You probably can't even withstand a single strike from the demons.

27:50.680 --> 27:52.180
How can I possibly

27:52.400 --> 27:54.620
entrust Wuyue Court to your hands?

28:01.070 --> 28:01.530
Slay!

28:11.550 --> 28:15.490
Get to know your enemy to beat them.

28:27.030 --> 28:28.570
Pure Spirit Physique.

28:31.640 --> 28:33.620
Lifer's pure spirit power.

28:42.070 --> 28:43.330
It's okay.

28:43.680 --> 28:44.770
Not bad. Okay.

28:45.750 --> 28:47.490
We barely escaped trouble

28:47.790 --> 28:49.250
this time.

28:49.920 --> 28:52.380
My biggest hope right now

28:52.400 --> 28:54.380
is that everyone on our peak

28:54.400 --> 28:56.730
stays put safely

28:56.790 --> 28:59.730
and never runs into demon spies.

29:00.000 --> 29:00.980
Master,

29:01.350 --> 29:03.900
the elders of other peaks make disciples patrol nonstop

29:04.070 --> 29:05.770
to find the demon spies.

29:06.070 --> 29:07.700
Why do you tell us to hide away?

29:07.920 --> 29:08.730
If people hear about this,

29:08.960 --> 29:10.010
they'll think Zhuiyu Peak

29:10.030 --> 29:11.250
can't hold its own.

29:11.720 --> 29:12.700
Don't talk nonsense.

29:12.720 --> 29:15.050
You're the senior,

29:15.240 --> 29:16.730
but you can't see the bigger picture.

29:17.720 --> 29:18.860
Who cares if people look up to us

29:18.880 --> 29:20.530
or look down on us?

29:20.880 --> 29:22.220
Staying alive is all that matters.

29:22.350 --> 29:23.330
With your skills,

29:23.350 --> 29:25.290
you even want to catch spies?

29:25.590 --> 29:26.620
You may get yourselves killed

29:26.640 --> 29:27.980
before catching anyone.

29:29.510 --> 29:30.860
Look at Lifei

29:30.880 --> 29:32.220
sitting right there.

29:32.510 --> 29:34.420
If Lei Xiuyuan hadn't

29:34.440 --> 29:35.620
helped her,

29:35.720 --> 29:37.940
she might've died.

29:38.750 --> 29:39.330
Master...

29:39.350 --> 29:40.290
One more thing.

29:43.960 --> 29:45.770
I've been up a whole day and night.

29:49.240 --> 29:51.290
Alright, go to bed early.

29:52.110 --> 29:55.090
Nothing's more important than staying alive.

29:55.200 --> 29:55.980
Master.

29:57.550 --> 29:59.010
Master, I'm not done talking.

30:04.880 --> 30:07.730
He keeps saving me, but I never appreciate it.

30:08.680 --> 30:09.490
I can't keep being like this.

30:13.480 --> 30:14.290
I have to get stronger

30:15.590 --> 30:16.460
and keep practicing.

30:31.270 --> 30:32.330
Why isn't it working this time?

30:37.440 --> 30:39.660
Take it easy. Don't freak out.

30:40.640 --> 30:41.860
Even bugs have their own way.

30:42.310 --> 30:43.460
There's a fix somewhere.

31:08.310 --> 31:09.530
Seems my practice has gone awry.

31:23.400 --> 31:24.010
Lifei.

31:24.920 --> 31:25.810
Qin.

31:28.310 --> 31:30.050
You practiced hastily and blocked your spirit meridians.

31:30.350 --> 31:31.570
Let me clear them for you.

31:41.110 --> 31:43.010
She really has the Pure Spirit Physique.

31:43.720 --> 31:45.900
By merging power with her,

31:46.270 --> 31:47.980
I'll master the spirit-absorbing art.

31:57.640 --> 32:00.090
Yangling, send me back now.

32:01.680 --> 32:03.530
You're totally drained right now.

32:03.920 --> 32:05.180
Let me help you.

32:07.200 --> 32:10.090
No. Master will be worried about me.

32:14.440 --> 32:15.090
Lifei.

32:27.880 --> 32:28.460
Lifei,

32:29.510 --> 32:30.730
your spirit aura has messed up.

32:31.200 --> 32:32.530
You can't even work the flying ribbon.

32:32.830 --> 32:34.330
Just rest and heal first, okay?

32:34.680 --> 32:36.730
Don't worry, I'll look after you.

32:38.920 --> 32:39.570
No need.

32:39.920 --> 32:40.420
Lifei.

32:40.440 --> 32:41.250
No, thanks.

32:41.480 --> 32:42.530
I've got to help you.

32:42.550 --> 32:43.770
You...

32:43.790 --> 32:45.220
Don't worry. Okay?

32:54.000 --> 32:55.620
Lifei, what happened?

32:57.750 --> 32:59.330
She practiced too hard, too fast,

32:59.350 --> 33:00.090
and messed up her spirit aura.

33:00.590 --> 33:02.250
I'll take her back and fix her blocked meridians.

33:02.550 --> 33:03.730
Where are you taking her?

33:06.110 --> 33:07.220
Cuihua Peak, of course.

33:07.680 --> 33:08.980
We've got loads of healing pills there.

33:09.400 --> 33:10.620
Baicao Peak is nearby.

33:11.030 --> 33:12.090
No need to seek afar.

33:12.440 --> 33:14.460
Lei, she's in really bad shape.

33:14.720 --> 33:16.140
Why do you keep getting in my way?

33:16.400 --> 33:19.140
Go to Baicao Peak for Mr. Dongyang.

33:22.720 --> 33:23.380
Lifei.

34:19.760 --> 34:21.740
Our sect's cultivation arts are brutal and intense.

34:22.070 --> 34:25.170
The fire flame arts are the trickiest to handle.

34:26.070 --> 34:28.570
Fire burns everything to nothing.

34:29.110 --> 34:31.860
If you practice half-heartedly with messy thoughts,

34:32.670 --> 34:34.530
you'll end up hurting yourself badly.

34:36.000 --> 34:36.900
I know I messed up.

34:39.670 --> 34:42.940
Lei Xiuyuan is protecting her, so Lifei should be alright.

34:49.030 --> 34:53.490
Unstable spirit aura, she's close to demonic backlash.

35:00.880 --> 35:03.690
Why is there demonic energy inside her?

35:04.550 --> 35:06.610
Demonic energy? How?

35:10.840 --> 35:13.610
Did those hidden demon spies in the court

35:14.110 --> 35:16.900
jump her at Yuelian Pond?

35:21.590 --> 35:23.460
Elder, can you clear the demonic energy?

35:24.360 --> 35:26.740
I'll try to clear it out.

35:38.480 --> 35:39.460
As you stand there

35:39.670 --> 35:41.690
like stone guards blocking the door,

35:42.110 --> 35:43.900
how am I supposed to treat her?

35:47.440 --> 35:49.260
Lei, I've got this covered.

35:49.800 --> 35:50.650
Head back first.

35:51.440 --> 35:52.260
I'll look after her.

35:52.840 --> 35:54.170
You may go.

35:54.920 --> 35:55.650
- I... - Enough.

35:56.590 --> 35:58.340
Lifei needs peace to heal.

35:58.960 --> 36:00.650
Both of you, step outside.

36:01.920 --> 36:02.420
Understood.

36:20.760 --> 36:21.460
Lei,

36:22.480 --> 36:24.650
I heard you've cut all ties with Lifei.

36:25.110 --> 36:26.130
I wonder why.

36:30.000 --> 36:31.650
This is between her and me.

36:32.440 --> 36:33.490
None of your business.

36:35.960 --> 36:37.090
Fair enough, not my business.

36:37.760 --> 36:39.610
But you keep clinging to her

36:39.630 --> 36:40.530
and upsetting her.

36:40.710 --> 36:41.690
That's out of line.

36:42.110 --> 36:43.010
What about you?

36:44.920 --> 36:47.650
You didn't look like you were healing her.

36:48.510 --> 36:49.340
Instead, it was like...

36:55.840 --> 36:56.690
I'm really curious.

36:57.110 --> 36:58.650
Yuelian Pond is locked with restriction spells.

36:59.400 --> 37:01.610
How did demon spies get inside?

37:04.480 --> 37:06.780
But you can go in and out anytime, too.

37:13.280 --> 37:15.570
As the spies are hanging around there,

37:16.110 --> 37:17.490
there's bound to be leads.

37:18.280 --> 37:20.170
I'll look into this carefully right now.

37:25.670 --> 37:26.340
Lei,

37:26.760 --> 37:28.460
you almost got poisoned by demonic energy.

37:28.800 --> 37:29.780
There might be residue in you.

37:30.070 --> 37:31.530
Better let Elder Dongyang check you out.

37:32.110 --> 37:33.380
I'll search the pond.

37:42.760 --> 37:43.460
Dongyang.

37:46.000 --> 37:47.090
Is Lifei alright?

37:48.710 --> 37:49.650
Take a look at this first.

37:57.320 --> 37:58.090
It

38:00.320 --> 38:03.380
looks just like Wuyue Court's seal.

38:04.400 --> 38:05.380
Who did this?

38:08.150 --> 38:10.300
The seal has gotten really weak.

38:10.670 --> 38:12.820
There's more than one seal in her,

38:13.360 --> 38:15.170
and they've been there ages.

38:16.070 --> 38:18.940
Can you tell what art made them?

38:21.070 --> 38:23.650
They're meant to hold back her spirit energy.

38:24.070 --> 38:27.570
Works in the same way as our spirit-binding seal.

38:29.360 --> 38:30.300
Spirit-binding seal?

38:31.400 --> 38:34.490
Isn't that the top immortal art to seal evil spirits?

38:37.190 --> 38:38.610
When I first met Lifei,

38:38.960 --> 38:41.300
she only knew a few basic small spells,

38:42.110 --> 38:45.130
but her energy has gotten so strong in the past year.

38:45.280 --> 38:47.050
She must've

38:47.440 --> 38:49.170
worn down the seals herself.

38:49.800 --> 38:52.380
No surprise she's changed so much.

38:53.960 --> 38:55.300
Maybe it was

38:55.320 --> 38:57.490
her former master, Wu Gen, whom she mentioned before,

38:57.510 --> 38:58.900
that did this.

39:11.280 --> 39:15.010
Whoever did this has insanely high cultivation

39:15.360 --> 39:18.980
and has some history with Wuyue Court.

39:22.190 --> 39:24.300
Let's stop guessing randomly.

39:24.670 --> 39:25.820
Ask her when she wakes up.

39:28.030 --> 39:30.530
When will she wake up?

39:31.400 --> 39:32.170
No clue.

39:33.110 --> 39:33.820
No clue?

39:33.840 --> 39:35.460
What do you mean?

39:36.550 --> 39:38.050
The demonic energy has been cleared,

39:38.230 --> 39:40.090
but she practices recklessly, damaging her spirit meridians.

39:40.550 --> 39:42.740
We need a Vermilion Fruit

39:43.230 --> 39:44.530
to cure her.

39:45.670 --> 39:47.650
The fruits are down in the spirit cave

39:47.760 --> 39:49.170
under Yuelian Pond,

39:50.070 --> 39:52.530
but loads of spirit creatures live down there,

39:52.670 --> 39:54.650
and the fruits are changeable.

39:55.510 --> 39:57.490
It's very hard to pick.

39:59.510 --> 40:00.980
She's your disciple,

40:01.510 --> 40:03.820
so you'll get the fruit.

40:04.670 --> 40:05.340
Sure, I will.

40:10.320 --> 40:12.740
Forget it, someone's heading there.

40:52.070 --> 40:55.610
The Sea Calamity is upon us. Don't ruin my plan.

40:57.320 --> 40:59.740
Lei, I'm sorry.

41:51.080 --> 41:54.510
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

41:55.240 --> 41:57.600
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

41:58.450 --> 42:00.080
♪The grand chapter is rewritten♪

42:00.280 --> 42:03.480
♪Startling the whole world♪

42:05.120 --> 42:08.370
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

42:08.610 --> 42:11.370
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

42:11.490 --> 42:14.880
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds, break through the waves♪

42:15.480 --> 42:17.850
♪ The heart's ocean knows no shore♪

42:18.050 --> 42:21.890
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

42:22.130 --> 42:25.250
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

42:25.640 --> 42:28.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water♪

42:29.440 --> 42:31.290
♪And falling petals♪

42:32.200 --> 42:36.600
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

42:42.200 --> 42:42.450
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.450 --> 42:44.720
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:57.220 --> 43:00.180
♪When fate calls, I rise as a worthy one♪

43:00.300 --> 43:02.940
♪I'll never back down♪

43:02.980 --> 43:08.980
♪I keep my former fearless resolve, never return it♪

43:09.460 --> 43:13.220
♪Dusk till dawn, I stay awake♪

43:13.340 --> 43:16.300
♪Bearing heavy missions, I ride far away♪

43:16.460 --> 43:21.140
♪The hidden fire in my heart forges a massive sword♪

43:21.300 --> 43:25.620
♪With you, we climb bleak cliffs beneath endless gloom♪

43:25.660 --> 43:27.860
♪Bow our heads and endure bitter gales♪

43:27.980 --> 43:33.980
♪Ambition surges; we hold new feasts amid thorns♪

43:34.180 --> 43:37.900
♪Climb high, lone sword sings, dance beneath autumn moon♪

43:38.020 --> 43:40.220
♪Dreams wane, then bloom full soon♪

43:40.340 --> 43:45.540
♪Rough the road, yet my steps shall never cease to move♪

43:46.340 --> 43:50.220
♪Banners wave, war drums thunder across the sky♪

43:50.340 --> 43:52.500
♪Sing everlasting verses♪

43:52.620 --> 43:58.780
♪A youth without passion is all in vain♪

44:11.020 --> 44:13.980
♪When fate calls, I rise as a worthy one♪

44:14.100 --> 44:16.740
♪I'll never back down♪

44:16.780 --> 44:22.780
